; Chapter 3 of The Little Schemer:; Cons the Magnificent;; Code examples assemled by Peteris Krumins (peter@catonmat.net).; His blog is at http://www.catonmat.net  --  good coders code, great reuse.;; Get yourself this wonderful book at Amazon: http://bit.ly/4GjWdP;; The rember function removes the first occurance of the given atom from the; given list.;(define rember  (lambda (a lat)    (cond      ((null? lat) '())      ((eq? (car lat) a) (cdr lat))      (else (cons (car lat)                  (rember a (cdr lat)))))))